OK ceviche.  Matador special a far cry from the delicious Peruvian BBQ chicken -- cook is not Peruvian!  Pescado a lo macho, OK.  Maduros (fried sweet plantains) delicious.  For dessert, Peruvian tasting OK.   Not happy that Peruvian cuisine is not properly prepared thus sending the wrong message to guests.  Next time I will just order 'arroz con maduros' (rice with sweet plantains)!  BTW:  management. ..Please, urgently pgrade bathrooms.
